OL,3,CGirl, 8, and man fighting for life
OL,4,Cafter van explosion outside pub
OL,6,FAn eight-year-old girl and a 43-year-
OL,7,Fold man are fighting for their lives
OL,8,Fafter the van they were in exploded
OL,9,Foutside a pub in West Yorkshire.
OL,11,FPolice were called to the Hare and
OL,12,FHounds on Liley Lane in Mirfield at
OL,13,F2.17pm on Sunday where five people had
OL,14,Fbeen hurt.
OL,16,FPictures of the aftermath of the blast
OL,17,Fshowed a burnt-out white van at the
OL,18,Fside of the road.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/2
