PN,33502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1782847102
OL,3,CGirl, 8, and man fighting for life
OL,4,Cafter van explosion outside pub
OL,6,FThe girl and the man were taken to
OL,7,Fhospital with life threatening
OL,8,Finjuries along with three other
OL,9,Fchildren who received life changing
OL,10,Finjuries.
OL,12,FAll had suffered serious burns.
OL,14,FPolice said their enquiries were
OL,15,Fongoing but that they are not thought
OL,16,Fto be any suspicious circumstances.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/2
